prodNameC: 馬丁彼得甲狀腺刺激激素診斷套組
ingredientsDesc: ANTI-HUMAN THYROID STIMULATING HORMONE COATED TUBES    These tubes are coated with an antibody having a high affinity for human thyroid stimulating hormone.   hTSH STANDARDS  Eight standards in a horse serum based matrix containing sodium azide and gentamicin sulfate are provided at the following concentrations: 0, 0.2, 0.5, 1, 5, 10, 25 and 50 μIU/mL referenced against the WHO 1st IRP 68/38.  WASH DILUENT (10X)  A phosphobuffered saline diluent containing Tween is supplied in a 10X concentrated form.  ANTI-hTSH 125I    This is an antibody labeled with 125I and generated against a different epitope of the hTSH molecule than the antibody bound to the tube. It is provided in a phosphobuffered saline diluent containing sodium azide as a preservative.
applicantAddr: 新竹縣寶山鄉新竹園區創新一路６號
efficacy: 為定量人類血清或血漿檢體中TSH濃度所設計的放射免疫分析法。
